infoboxbuilder-desc: InfoboxBuilder is a tool that allows users to build Lua-based infoboxes without any programming skills and to use custom Lua modules for logical operations on demand.
infoboxbuilder-errors-desc: Something may not work as intended. More info:
infoboxbuilder-errors-no-module: Your custom module does not seem to exist. Check the given name for typos and make sure it contains a Module: prefix.
